title: Heathrow traffic and business commentary September 2015 (Heathrow Airport Holdings Limited)
text: ( Source : Heathrow Airport Holdings Limited ) Heathrow - keeping Britain moving forward A record 6.77 million passengers (+2.9% on September 2014 ) travelled through Heathrow on 40,292 flights in September 2015 , making it the busiest September
